  "texts": [
    "In iterating, we employed methodological triangulation by analysing data from multiple angles, such as comparing interpretations of RAI practices or high-risk settings across diverse settings and AI roles of all included articles.",
    "Group consensus was used to resolve any disagreements by revisiting original articles for clarification and validation.",
    "Results Summary of the 45 included articlesThe majority of the 45 included articles (88.89%) were published after the year 2020 (Fig. 2).",
    "When disclosed, the articles collected data most commonly in the USA (24.44%) and multiple countries (22.22%) (Fig. 3).",
    "Multiple countries were selected when the data was reported from more than one country or a geographical region encompassing more than one country."
  ]
}